### Cancel
If you just want to cancel the a repeated scheduled task, you can just do like following (here is a [runnable demo][1] in my repo):

    @Autowired
    private ScheduledAnnotationBeanPostProcessor postProcessor;
    @Autowired
    private TestSchedule testSchedule;

    public void later() {
        postProcessor.postProcessBeforeDestruction(test, &quot;testSchedule&quot;);
    }

